      • isNextToken

        protected boolean isNextToken(TokenType _type)
        Returns true if the next element in the token list iterator is of the given type. The iterator's cursor is not affected. If there is no next element, returns false.
        Parameters:
        _type - the token type to match
        Returns:
        true if the next element matches the given type, false if it does not, or if there is no next element
